songs.title: Numb
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
I saw you cry today
The pain may fill you
I saw you shy away
The pain will not kill you
You made me smile today
You spoke with many voices
We traveled miles today
Shared expressions voiceless

[Refrain 1]
It has to end

[Chorus]
Living in your head
Without anything to numb you
Living on the edge
Without anything to numb you

[Refrain 2]
It has to end to begin

[Verse 2]
Began and end today
Gave and got given
You made a friend today
Kindred soul cracked spirit

[Refrain 2]
It has to end to begin

[Chorus]
Living in your head
Without anything to numb you
Living on the edge
Without anything to numb you

[Refrain 3]
It had to end to begin

[Chorus] (x2)
Living in your head
Without anything to numb you
Living on the edge
Without anything to numb you

[Outro]
It has begun
